The state needs to be abit more strongly typed. Its trying to cast your initial state from type `any` to type `never`.

When creating the default state for the data you should define an interface for your state, here&#39;s an example for a todo list array:

    interface IAppState {
      toDoList: any[];
    }
    const initialState: IAppState = {
      toDoList: []
    };
    
    export default function reducer(state = initialState, action) {}

